A
E[X\mid A]
P(X>3)=(1-p)^4
k=0,1,2,3
P(X=k\mid X>3)=0
k=4,5,\ldots
 P(X=k)=p(1-p)^k,\quad k=0,1,2,\ldots 
 P(X=k\mid X>3)=\frac{P(X=k,X>3)}{P(X>3)}=\frac{P(X=k)}{P(X>3)}=p(1-p)^{k-4}. 
 E[X\mid X>3]=\sum_{k=4}^\infty kP(X=k\mid X>3)=\sum_{k=4}^\infty kp(1-p)^{k-4}=\sum_{k=0}^\infty (k+4)p(1-p)^k=4+E[X]. 
